snippet.title: Be Zero : new original number puzzle with sci-fi style
snippet.description:
"Be Zero" is a new original number puzzle with sci-fi style.
Make every number to be zero!

Best game for math puzzle fans.
Best game for sci-fi, Hi-Tech lovers.

I promise it is addictive and unique.
I promise it is worth the price.

Infinite levels!

Please support original game. Thank you.

iOS: 
https://itunes.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1367099276?pt=118326071&ct=youtube&mt=8

Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xydw.f9
